text.tspan: Population whose cause of death is registered
The estimated share of people in each country whose cause of death is registered in the national vital

registration system
. If all deaths were registered with a cause of death, the chart area would be full.
Data source: World Health Organization - Global Health Observatory (2025)
Note: Data points are taken as single-year observations between 2007 and 2016, depending on the country. The total number of deaths is
estimated using data from household surveys and censuses.
